{"tid":2209704,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[21歲] 信義威秀長髮女遭人潑屎！「一桶砸下」萬人看傻眼　她竟不提告","createTime":"2020-09-19T20:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T22:03:32.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"59655132ee355aefa827fe660ff14a5c0e5f0ffd","tid":2209704,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T20:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5152/d5152047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5152%2Fd5152047.jpg&h=5a3d0a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台北市信義威秀影城19日深夜發生潑屎事件，一名身穿黑色衣服、藍色牛仔短褲21歲邱姓女子遭人當街潑灑穢物，造成現場瞬間瀰漫劇烈惡臭。警方表示，由於潑屎現場屬公共場所，後續將調閱監視畫面，約談動手的男子到案說明。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，事件發生在19日深夜10時許，邱女在信義威秀遭男子潑灑穢物，員警趕到現場後先協助對方清潔，邱女才向警方供稱「不認識動手的男子」，並表示不願提告後就自行離去。<br />\n<br />\n照片在臉書「爆料公社」曝光後，吸引超過1.6萬人按讚討論，有人說「不管什麼原因，潑排泄物實在讓人受不了，不只讓被潑的難堪，也造成別人的困擾」、「太噁心人了吧」、「小妹妹怎麼受得了，超污辱人的」、「屎要裝成一桶也不簡單。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5152/d5152059.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5152%2Fd5152059.jpg&h=58cc0c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5152/d5152057.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5152%2Fd5152057.jpg&h=4d461e1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1834e84d47cf5d528134b1c7cb449b128478f085","tid":2209704,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T20:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3hvCMqb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3hvCMqb.jpg&h=4c767b3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a1bfaa21e9376439fc67a6cfea0a8cfb3fcbf65","tid":2209704,"uid":303464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T20:13:11.000Z","msg":"呢啲就有高清圖"},{"pid":"a02775b87f18c317ab653dc6d88ff5f61850ef56","tid":2209704,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20